	 display N1 |  display C8
	 TMAX=5 |  DT=0.00005 |  NN=10001 |  --    timing               
	 scale=2.5
	 ---------------------------------------------                     
	 x=0.7 |  --           initial value for input
	 a=0.25 |  --           deadspace for backlash                    
